N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 175-1.3 - Order of the director of the division for youth

State Regulations

Transfers pursuant to this Subpart may be made only upon
written order of the Director of the Division for Youth and upon the written
consent or approval of the Commissioner of the Office of Mental Health or the

Office of Mental Retardation and Developmental Disabilities. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9
§§
175-1.3

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
